OL,5, Divorcing teachers and NHS staff face  
OL,6, delays to their financial settlements  
OL,7, while the Treasury recalculates public 
OL,8, sector pensions.                       
OL,10,FBoth current and retired staff are     
OL,11,Faffected, risking a "severe and        
OL,12,Fdrastic" impact on thousands of        
OL,13,Fdivorcing couples, say solicitors.     
OL,15,FOne woman told BBC News she was not    
OL,16,Fexpecting the change and has been      
OL,17,Funable to move home.                   
OL,19,FThe Treasury announced the delay in    
OL,20,FMarch, promising a solution by summer. 
